beer.beer_description:
Lime Crisis kicks off our 2018 Rare Breed season with plenty of action!  

We’re levelling up our Double IPA offerings with an ABV of 8.2%, 
crushed Persian black limes and Himalayan rock salt in the whirlpool and tank-busting dosages of Citra, Centennial, Wakatu and Taiheke hops.  

This is one beer that will have you ready to RELOAD.

APPEARANCE: Light golden. 

AROMA: A blend of citrus aromas from the use of Persian black limes and a blend of US and NZ hops.

FLAVOUR: Deceptively light bodied with strong hop bitterness, mild spice notes and a rounded mineral finish from the Himalayan rock salt.
